Initial release: SEO Machine - Open source SEO content creation tool
Transform Castos Writer into SEO Machine - a generalized, open-source tool
for creating long-form, SEO-optimized blog content for any business.

## What's New

- **Generic Templates**: All context files converted to fill-in-the-blank templates
- **Real Example**: Original Castos setup moved to examples/castos/ as reference
- **Complete Documentation**: Updated README, Quick Start, and NEXT-STEPS guides
- **Environment Setup**: Added .env.example with detailed configuration instructions
- **Open Source**: MIT License with contribution guidelines

## Key Features

- Custom Claude Code commands: /research, /write, /rewrite, /optimize, /analyze-existing
- Specialized AI agents: SEO optimizer, meta creator, internal linker, keyword mapper
- Advanced analysis modules: Search intent, keyword density, readability, SEO quality
- Data integrations: Google Analytics 4, Search Console, DataForSEO
- Template-driven: Easy to customize for any brand or industry

## What Changed from Castos Writer

- Removed all Castos-specific branding and content
- Created template files for brand-voice, features, writing-examples, internal-links
- Added examples/castos/ directory with complete real-world example
- Updated all commands and agents to be industry-agnostic
- Generalized documentation for any business use case
